column2: Modifying an object obtained via a user-controlled property name may lead to accidental mutation of the built-in Object prototype, and possibly escalate to remote code execution or cross-site scripting.
column4: This assignment may alter Object.prototype if a malicious '__proto__' string is injected from [["user controlled input"|"relative:///VulnFinder-CodeQL-main/src/javascript-cwe/CWE-915/examples/PrototypePollutingAssignment.js:5:14:5:26"]].
